Always had fun working with Salman: SRK on 'Tubelight' cameo.
Shah Rukh Khan and Salman Khan coming together in Kabir Khan's Tubelight is probably the biggest news of the year. Fans of the two Khan-doms are super excited to see their favourite superstars share screen space, but the makers surprisingly did not cash in on this. After a lot of speculation, Kabir Khan posted a photo confirming SRK's cameo on Instagram, without much fanfare.ALSO READ: Tubelight director Kabir Khan shares Shah Rukh's look from Salman's filmALSO READ: Shah Rukh Khan says he can't compete with Salman Khan at the box office